query:
SELECT io.output
                    FROM tensorzero.chat_inferences i
                    INNER JOIN tensorzero.chat_inference_data io ON io.id = i.id AND io.created_at = i.created_at
                    WHERE i.id = $1
                      AND i.episode_id = $2
                      AND i.function_name = $3
                      AND i.variant_name = $4
                    LIMIT 1
